883f0342b70","tid":257102,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>港珠澳最on鳩係大陸D港口過晒香港先整.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該早就起<br />\n仲要有咁矮起咁矮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點起得矮? <br />\n頂盡雙程雙線(你唔係想2+1路下話?), 未必批 <br />\n重認為應該起... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42faaf885e21fd95700f5e5ef22b3ca7729ffe5e","tid":257102,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:14:56.000Z","msg":"放寬揸自己私家車過大陸都驚啦，保險點計，遇到撞車黨同埋扮被撞嘅屈錢黨點算"},{"pid":"a1d701db5de334d6ff4f22f3e5c253ca3086b0fd","tid":257102,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:15:09.000Z","msg":"條橋三年之後仲係度先同我講啦"},{"pid":"0bf3ef38d328ece614b737259134ca9340bd55c4","tid":257102,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T18:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>港珠澳最on鳩係大陸D港口過晒香港先整.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該早就起<br />\n仲要有咁矮起咁矮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點起得矮? <br />\n頂盡雙程雙線(你唔係想2+1路下話?), 未必批 <br />\n重認為應該起... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我講如果改革開放初期起<br />\n果時廣州/深圳都無港口<br />\n有咁矮我講高度<br />\n起得矮等大船過唔到<br />\n好似南京長江大橋<br />\n當年起只有24米高<br />\n明明三峽水壩起好可行大船<br />\n因為條橋頂住只可行細船<br />\n南京又多多藉口唔肯拆橋<br />\n梗係唔拆啦<br />\n拆左D船直駛去重慶都得<br />\n一日唔拆橋<br />\n大船都要南京落貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354aad5efad43b37e178e23607d09369aed4582f","tid":257102,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T18:35:11.000Z","msg":"條橋頂撚到50年先算啦"}]}